sub_title: Student Well-being Officer - Faculty of Economics and Business - University of Groningen
summary:
As FEB student well-being officer my mission is to contribute to a positive, inclusive and safe academic environment where every student within FEB community feels heard, seen, and included.

Together with other stakeholders within FEB we are working on different initiatives, which help the students to succeed while focusing on improving their well-being, so the students can thrive academically, but also in their personal and professional lives after graduation.
